Sublime

Move file between groups:
ctrl + shift + 1 : move to group 1

Switch focus between groups:
Ctrl + 1 : move focus to group 1

Split views:
Alt + Shift + 2 : split view into 2 columns

top:
<, > to change sort order
shift + w to save settings to ~/.toprc


show desktop: control + windows + D
show all open windows: windows + W

stop X: sudo service lightdm stop

Debian packages:
install: sudo dpkg -i DEB_PACKAGE
remove: sudo dpkg -r package_name
search: apt-cache search name

GRUB update:
sudo nano /etc/default/grub
sudo update-grub

Search for packages:

apt-cache search keyword

List installed:
sudo apt list --installed


Update all packages:

sudo apt-get update        # Fetches the list of available updates
sudo apt-get upgrade       # Strictly upgrades the current packages
sudo apt-get dist-upgrade  # Installs updates (new ones)

